title: Merlin's Apprentice - Part 1
description:
Merlin returns to find that chaos reigns over the land and that the lady of the lake has begun to cast her spell over some tribal warriors.  The only hope for Camelot and it&#039;s people lies with a thief, who begins to exhibit strange and wonderful powers.  Merlin must teach his new apprentice how to control his new gift to stop the world becoming all that is evil.  Sam Neill returns for the second time as the master sorcerer, Merlin.

PART 2 WILL FOLLOW.
